                      <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-2xl bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-emerald-500"
                      >
                        {selectedPackage.officialIssue.alreadyIssued ? "Registrar reemissao oficial" : "Emitir oficialmente"}
                      </button>
                    </form>
                  ) : null}
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </>
      ) : (
        <article class="rounded-[32px] border border-slate-950/8 bg-white p-6 shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(15,23,42,0.06)]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-amber-500/10 p-3 text-amber-700">
              <AlertTriangle className="size-5" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-slate-500">Workspace vazia</p>
              <h2 class="mt-1 font-display text-2xl tracking-tight text-slate-950">Selecione um caso da fila</h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-600">
            O recorte atual nao trouxe nenhum laudo elegivel para abrir a thread detalhada. Ajuste os filtros ou limpe
            a busca para carregar um caso ativo da mesa.
          </p>
        </article>
      )}
    </div>
  </section>
</ReviewerShellLayout>
